about me
Hello everyone I am from Germany and my name is Tobias, feel free to call me Tobi.
Im 19 years old and my birthday is in february the 12th
I live in southern Germany in a city called Stuttgart
(About two hours away from Switzerland and about one and a half hours away from France by car)

In my current freetime im watching tons of Animes from this season and read popular Mangas like Dice;The Gamer and Area D.
Also i play some games, these are Osu!, Love Live! School Idol Festival (LLSIF), Phantasy Star Online 2 JP and I wanna be the Guy Fangames.
In the past i used to play LoL, Elsword, Warframe and CsGo.

If you want to play something together with me feel free to ask me!
